<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.2">
<l>paṟṟumañ caḷpūcip pāvaimā roṭupā ṭiyil</l>
<l>ciṟṟil citaitteṅkum tīmai ceytu tiriyāmē</l>
<l>kaṟṟuttū ḷiyuṭai vēṭarkā ṉiṭaik kaṉṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>eṟṟukkeṉ piḷḷaiyaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To stop him from wandering everywhere,</l>
<l rend="indent">getting up to mischief in the village,</l>
<l>Destroying the sand houses along with the girls</l>
<l rend="indent">besmeared with lasting turmeric [paste],</l>
<l>Why did I send my child after the calves into the midst of the forest</l>
<l rend="indent">with hunters and dust from the claves?</l>
<l>Ah! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
